<collectingCountry box="[362,464,1707,1731]" name="Uruguay" pageId="8" pageNumber="211">Uruguay</collectingCountry>
: Montevideo (according to 
<bibRefCitation author="Persson" box="[786,961,1706,1730]" pageId="8" pageNumber="211" refString="Persson, P. I. (1971) &quot; Eugenies resa &quot;. Localities, dates and labels of the insects collected during the voyage around the world by the Swedish frigate &quot; Eugenie &quot; in the years 1851 - 1853. Entomologish Tidskrift, 92, 164 - 172." type="journal article" year="1971">
